---
// Sustainability.astro
// Section id: #sustainability
// JS binds to: #sustainability-hero, #sustainability-hero-inner,
// #sustainability-tagline, #sustainability-title, #sustainability-title-pre,
// #sustainability-title-main, #sustainability-desc,
// #sustainability-items, .sustainability-item, .sustainability-item-num,
// #sustainability-rive-canvas-harvesting, #sustainability-rive-canvas-text.
// All ids, classes, and data-* attributes are preserved verbatim.
---

<div id="sustainability" class="section">
  <div class="section__inner o-container">

    <!-- Hero text block -->
    <div id="sustainability-hero">
      <div id="sustainability-hero-inner">
        <div id="sustainability-tagline" class="sub2">100% Plant-based</div>
        <div id="sustainability-title">
          <h4 id="sustainability-title-pre">Vegan-friendly</h4>
          <h2 id="sustainability-title-main">sustainability</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="sustainability-desc" class="body2">
          Pure cork sourced sustainably. <br />Completely vegan — no cows were harmed,
          <br />but it might be full of "bull"sh*t.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three stat items -->
    <div id="sustainability-items" class="o-grid">

      <!-- Item 1: first harvest age -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h3 class="sustainability-item-title">Average <br />age of first <br />harvest</h3>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          Cork oaks are typically first harvested at around 25 years, once the bark is thick enough to remove safely.
        </div>
        <div class="sustainability-item-num">25</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2: harvesting interval — Rive animation canvas -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h4 class="sustainability-item-title">Harvesting <br />interval</h4>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          After each harvest, the bark takes about 9 years to regrow, making cork a renewable material.
        </div>
        <canvas id="sustainability-rive-canvas-harvesting"></canvas>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3: power draw — Rive animation canvas -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h4 class="sustainability-item-title">Power draw <br />while in use</h4>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          No compute. No tokens. So you can say "please" and "thank you" as much as you want, guilt free.
        </div>
        <canvas id="sustainability-rive-canvas-text"></canvas>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>